race.description: Grab Life By The Balls Handicap (C1)
race.comment: IN SOCIETY (6) goes well for Melbourne Cup winning hoop Dolan who has a win and three placings from five steers and will be high on confidence following that last-start Eagle Farm victory. Will be right there when the judge calls a halt. ARTSPACE (2) will be ready to peak now third-up from the spell and the step-up to the mile suits. Should be hitting the line with gusto. BROOKLYN DAISY (5) was a touch plain last time out but the four placings prior to start the campaign were good enough for this. Worth another chance. BOLD ARTIC (3) has only missed a drum once in five spins around this circuit and gets in well at the weights with the 3kg claim. In the mix. MAKAMAE (12) is a former Victorian having her first run for the new yard and any market push should be noted.
